{"type": "article", "id": 17320, "title": "水泥灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-10T06:20:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071224340mi18anQdAevJUCj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t水泥灯是近段时间的热门，暖黄灯光下的水泥非常柔和，不再令人感到冰冷。这盏水泥灯只有一半的灯罩，有点像拆下来的壁灯，它是通过旋转灯罩来调整光线强弱。当需要看书时，就将灯旋转到正面，反之，需要休息或弱光时，就让灯泡背对自己。水泥材料让灯罩和灯座浑然一体，上面有自然的气孔，在光线照射下有格外柔和的效果，带给人踏实温暖的家的感受。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144422AwZeOnBdXhoVKJH3.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"601\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.00166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144422xCrApMmc7v3jKuiX.jpg\" width=\"914\" height=\"1280\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.40043764\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144423y6uNl4JUH9FGVEx8.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144424wRKW16qGknX3Egyr.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}